â–¶ï¸ How the System Works
1ï¸âƒ£ Face Registration

User enters UID and Name

Camera captures multiple face samples

Images are stored in a unique folder:

dataset/UID_Name/

2ï¸âƒ£ Face Recognition

LBPH model is trained on all registered faces

Live camera feed is compared against trained data

Recognized faces are matched with UID & Name

3ï¸âƒ£ Attendance Marking

Punch In â†’ records time in PunchIn

Punch Out â†’ updates PunchOut

Attendance is stored in a structured CSV file

